\begin_inset LatexCommand \label{5pointalgo}

\end_inset 

(
\begin_inset Formula $5-$
\end_inset 

point Dyadic Subdivision Scheme) For a given integer 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset 

, begin with some initial 
\begin_inset Formula $y-$
\end_inset 

values 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{j,k}\, k\in \Z $
\end_inset 

 over dyadic numbers 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{j,k}=k/2^{j}$
\end_inset 

, 
\begin_deeper 
\layout Enumerate

recopy data at 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{j+1,2k}=x_{j,k}$
\end_inset 

: 
