\begin_inset Formula $M_{j+1}\leq \max _{l=0,1}\left\{ \sum _{k\in \Z }\left|\gamma _{2k-l}\right|\right\} M_{j}$
\end_inset 

 because 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{j+1,2l}=\sum _{k\in \Z }\gamma _{2k-2l}y_{j,k}$
\end_inset 

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{j+1,2l+1}=\sum _{k\in \Z }\gamma _{2k-2l-1}y_{j,k}$
\end_inset 

.
