\begin_inset Formula $y_{j+1,2l+1}=\sum _{k\in \Z }\gamma _{4k-2l-1}^{(1)}y_{j,2k}+\gamma _{4k-2l}^{(2)}y_{j,2k+1}$
\end_inset 

.
 Thus if 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda _{HR}=\max _{l=0,1}\left\{ \sum _{k\in \Z }\left|\gamma _{2k-l}^{(1)}\right|+\left|\gamma _{2k+1-l}^{(2)}\right|\right\} $
